{"tid":1721650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Poly同學仔話要送物資就唔會今日送啦","createTime":"2019-11-14T17:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:35:21.000Z","uid":140932,"like":264,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"51278568974297584ccc0e5d3ff523cfeb2ccec1","tid":1721650,"uid":140932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"大概夜晚十一點左右poly舊canteen發生左一場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">捉鬼事件</span> <br />\n<br />\n今日我係幫手送物資入黎poly 無耐就有人開大聲公嗌話有鬼 然後就開始好似沙士咁封佐所有出入口 一開頭好似審犯咁叫所有人舉高雙手 之後只安排三個出入口搜身check 身入證學生證 <br />\n<br />\n我同另外兩個女仔係canteen排隊準備出去 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搜正門有個男仔兇9我地叫我地行撚快d係超大聲</span></span></strong> 首先我明白你地驚 你地要捉鬼都算 唔該你地班poly學生唔需要兇9手足 成班FA 記者 送物資既朋友就係企門 之後就開始有班人起哄場面相當混亂 我哋臨走嗰陣仲有一班前線攞曬武器衝入去想斬人咁款相當意氣用事 仲差小小發生打鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 前前後後搞佐個幾兩個鐘 希望今日係poly捉鬼既人可以檢討下 大家都係想幫手希望你地可以容氣小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其次 我地臨走戈陣已經相當谷氣 有一班坐左係近canteen 門口有個樓梯位 我講咗句話如果你地再咁捉鬼唔會再有人送物資過黎 然後有個唔知係咪poly既男學生無戴口罩講左句 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地要送物資就唔會今日先黎送啊？</span></span></span></strong>  唔該都無聲就當老奉？我真係鄭重咁講聲我地唔會再出錢出力送黎poly 送都送去其他大專院校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日你地話物資夠唔洗再送 今日又話咩咩物資唔夠要物資又要人 真心嬲到癲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個係poly負責做哨兵既男仔同我地講 話今日都唔止得3個鬼入佐黎 計埋無公佈既加加埋埋都起馬30個 如果你地咁想捉鬼而搞到成班人士氣低落 你地可以繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人有個小小建議係如果你地真係要捉 正係封canteen有咩用你要捉就連所有出入口都要封 班便衣係有受訓練架唔係咁易比你捉到 如果佢地有心連學生證都可以偽造<br />\n間間學校你開放得比所有人就一定會有鬼 你地再曬時間咁捉鬼 相信你地好快唔洗比曱甴打 已經可以自己鬼打鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS: 前日同琴日我都係city 感謝有位city學生比我地入你間房訓陣 如果唔係我地就要訓地下 cit學生超有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7da1d279f5cce7cb329cf74806b6250865677b0","tid":1721650,"uid":337761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Twitter吹大雞！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">！！！McConnell支持法案，重點推 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=1d2d93c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&h=8c1d25b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick 多謝 McConnell <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1195011922799804416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1195011922799804416&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=cffc8155\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1195011922799804416&h=d2960883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1195011922799804416</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Hawley 多謝 McConnell<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1194998439723065345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1194998439723065345&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=d42c692d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1194998439723065345&h=07e17f14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: